    "long_instructions": "### Wherever Whenever\r\n\r\n**Define:** You've been hired to add effects to this remix of Wherever Whenever by Shakira. Your requirements are:\r\n- No changes to the lead vocals\r\n- All backing vocals should have a delay\r\n- All acoustic guitar tracks should be at medium volume\r\n- Each acoustic guitar track should have a different effect\r\n\r\nYou will only need to add effect blocks to the code - the rest of the song is locked!\r\n\r\n**Prepare:** Plan where you will add your effects\r\n\r\n**Try:** Code your song! Listen to the example for an idea of what it could sound like!\r\n<div style=\"background:#ebe8f1; border: 0; border-radius: 10px; clear:both; padding: 5px\">\r\n\r\nNeed some help? Try the [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-book\"></i> Docs](#clickable=documentation-button) in the upper-right corner!\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n**Reflect:** Make sure your code has:\r\n\r\n- At least 6 effect blocks",
